VGA_demo
------------------

Simple demo showing use of VGA on altera DE1 use switches [8:0] to control colour.
3 bits from the switches controls the HIGH bits of the 4bit DAC on each VGA colour channel.
Try making the colours functions of x,y for pretty effects.
http://letshackstuff.com/?s=blog&m=permalink&x=vga-output-from-the-de1